Output docs/demo/tui.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 740
Set Height 440
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set Padding 24
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "export HOME=/tmp/gnbd-tui"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "gnb"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 700ms

Type "/"
Sleep 300ms
Type "deploy"
Sleep 2s

Escape
Sleep 500ms

Type "t"
Sleep 1s
Type "t"
Sleep 1s
Type "t"
Sleep 700ms

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
